title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 8 2022
description:
NYT writes off Stacey Abrams, reveals her own internal polling shows her cratering with black men. Clay and Buck disagree on whether the GOP has an opportunity to win over black men. Queen Elizabeth II dies at 96. The NY Post's Miranda Devine joins Clay and Buck to discuss the breaking news on the Queen's death and the very latest on the FBI coverup of Hunter Biden's crimes. Who's still wearing masks on planes? Rand Paul on Fauci.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
